<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/6638-this-book-exists-because-card-couldn-t">This book exists because Card couldn&#39;t edit Shadow Puppets down to a reasonable length. Less &quot;interesting world events speculation,&quot; more &quot;tedious wishful thinking.&quot; By the way, did you know that Bean and Achilles were at battle school together? And that battle school children share a special bond?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_6638'><a id="like_count_community_question_6638" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/6638?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F8647.Shadow_of_the_Giant">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/6638-this-book-exists-because-card-couldn-t">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
